# Environment Variables

# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# WEBFLOW_API_TOKEN
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Your Webflow Workspace API token. Required for `npm run webflow:import`.
#
# How to get your token:
#   1. Go to https://webflow.com/dashboard/account/api
#   2. Click "Generate API token"
#   3. Ensure the token has "Code Components" write access on your Workspace
#
# If this variable is missing or empty, the Webflow CLI will automatically
# open a browser window for OAuth-based Workspace authorisation instead.
#
# ⚠️  NEVER commit this file with a real token. `.env` is already in .gitignore.
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
WEBFLOW_API_TOKEN="your_token_here"
